  <brief_title>The Effects of Gastric Tube on the Quality of Life and Nutritional Status After Ivor-Lewis Esophagectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effects of Gastric Tube on the Quality of Life and Nutritional Status After Ivor-Lewis Esophagectomy: A Randomized Control Trial and Physiological Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
